(firstQuint)Postmarketing Study to Determine Performance of the SIGMA HP PARTIAL KNEE SYSTEM.

 The purpose of this study is to collect more information about the Sigma HP(R) Partial Knee System made by DePuy International.

 The aim of this study is to measure how this particular type of knee replacement performs over a two year period.

